>>In high dimensional space, what is a manifold?<<
( ) The dimensionality of the dataset {{A manifold has a dimensionality, but it is not a dimensionality itself.}}
( ) An unsupervised learning method  {{Manifold learning is an unsupervised dimensionality reduction method, but a manifold on its own is not a learning method.}}
(x) A lower dimensional space that supports the characteristics of the data distribution
